data.description: Incredible 2.72-acre property with 6 beds, 2 baths, and endless potential! The home features a warm and inviting 16x11 enclosed front porch, the perfect spot for relaxing. Step inside where the red pine wood flooring stuns the downstairs. The eat-in kitchen is large enough for entertaining and offering an abundance of storage space. The first floor offers the primary bedroom and a secondary bedroom. The 4 remaining spacious bedrooms are upstairs. While it may require some repairs, the potential this property holds is truly worth exploring. The surrounding 2.72 acres provide ample space for expansion, landscaping, or even the addition of your dream outdoor amenities. Solar panels are owned and will come with the home. Electric bill runs approximately $30/month. Conveniently located near 59 and to all the amenities that Shepherd and Cleveland have to offer. Schedule your tour today and don't miss out on this rare chance to own a slice of country paradise!
